Description: 
        📦 rex-plus (for humans)
        =======================
        
        Plus version of re
        
        Installation
        -----
        
        ```bash
        pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ --extra-index-url https://pypi.org/simple/ rex-plus
        ```
        
        Example
        -----
        
        ```python
        import rex_plus
        # Partial replacement according to regular expression
        text = rex_plus.sub('(我是)有人吗', ['卧室'], '我是有人吗')
        # output: 卧室有人吗
        ```
        
